#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:accountant_knowledge.accountant_knowledge_article_template_attestation
msgid ""
"As a result of these findings, and due to their significant effect, we are "
"unable to confirm the overall consistency and plausibility of the interim "
"financial statements attached to this statement."
msgstr ""
"ເນື່ອງຈາກຜົນການກວດພົບເຫຼົ່ານີ້, ແລະ ຍ້ອນຜົນກະທົບທີ່ສຳຄັນຂອງມັນ, ພວກເຮົາບໍ່ສາມາດຢືນຢັນຄວາມສອດຄ່ອງ ແລ"
"ະ ຄວາມເປັນໄປໄດ້ໂດຍລວມຂອງໃບລາຍງານການເງິນຊົ່ວຄາວທີ່ຄັດຕິດມານີ້ໄດ້."

#. module: accountant_knowledge
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:accountant_knowledge.accountant_knowledge_article_template_attestation
msgid ""
"As chartered accountants, we have carried out a compilation of the interim "
"financial statements of {{ company name }} for the period from {{ start of "
"period }} to {{ end of period }}, which include the following key figures:"
msgstr ""
"ໃນນາມນັກບັນຊີທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບອະນຸຍາດ, ພວກເຮົາໄດ້ດຳເນີນການຮວບຮວມໃບລາຍງານການເງິນຊົ່ວຄາວຂອງ {{ "
"company name }} ສຳລັບໄລຍະເວລາແຕ່ {{ start of period }} ຫາ {{ end of period }}, "
"ເຊິ່ງລວມມີຕົວເລກທີ່ສຳຄັນດັ່ງນີ້:"

