"ຫາກການປ່ຽນແປງໄດ້ຖືກນຳໃຊ້ແບບມີຜົນໄປຂ້າງໜ້າ (prospective), ໃຫ້ອະທິບາຍເຫດຜົນ ແລະ ລະບຸຜົນກະທົບຕໍ່"
"ລາຍການທີ່ສຳຄັນຂອງໄລຍະເວລານີ້, ເວັ້ນເສຍແຕ່ຈະບໍ່ສາມາດກຳນົດໄດ້."

#. module: accountant_knowledge
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:accountant_knowledge.accountant_knowledge_article_template_changes_in_accounting_policies
msgid ""
"If the change has been applied retrospectively, present the main items from "
"prior periods restated under the new accounting method."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກການປ່ຽນແປງໄດ້ຖືກນຳໃຊ້ແບບມີຜົນຍ້ອນຫຼັງ (retrospective), ໃຫ້ສະແດງລາຍການທີ່ສຳຄັນຈາກໄລຍະເວລ"
"າກ່ອນທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບການປັບປຸງພາຍໃຕ້ວິທີການບັນຊີໃໝ່."

#. module: accountant_knowledge
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:accountant_knowledge.accountant_knowledge_article_template_changes_in_accounting_policies
msgid ""
"If the change was applied <strong>prospectively</strong>, describe its "
